#. <section class="sutta" id="sn50.55"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 50"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 50"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:0.2"
msgid "6. Punagaṅgāpeyyālavagga"
msgstr "6. Another Chapter of Abbreviated Texts on the Ganges, Etc."

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:0.3"
msgid "55–​66. Pācīnādisutta"
msgstr "55–66. Sloping East, Etc."

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.252"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gaṅgā nadī pācīnaninnā pācīnapoṇā pācīnapabbhārā;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, the Ganges river slants, slopes, and inclines to the east."

msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañca balāni bhāvento pañca balāni "
"bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, a mendicant who develops and cultivates the five powers "
"slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañca balāni bhāvento pañca balāni "
"bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant who develops the five powers slant, slope, and "
"incline to extinguishment?"

msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.4"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu, saddhābalaṃ bhāveti rāgavinayapariyosānaṃ "
"dosavinayapariyosānaṃ mohavinayapariyosānaṃ …"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the powers of faith, energy, mindfulness, "
"immersion, and wisdom, which culminate in the removal of greed, hate, and "
"delusion."

msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.5"
msgid ""
"evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pañca balāni bhāvento pañca balāni "
"bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo nibbānapabbhāro”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant who develops and cultivates the five powers slants, "
"slopes, and inclines to extinguishment.”"

msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.6"
msgid "Vitthāretabbā."
msgstr ""
"(To be expanded for each of the different rivers as in SN 45.91–102, removal "
"of greed version.)"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.7"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:1.8"
msgid "Gaṅgāpeyyālavaggo chaṭṭho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:2.1"
msgid "Cha pācīnato ninnā,"
msgstr "Six on slanting to the east,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:2.2"
msgid "cha ninnā ca samuddato;"
msgstr "and six on slanting to the ocean;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:2.3"
msgid "Dvete cha dvādasa honti,"
msgstr "these two sixes make twelve,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn50.55-66:2.4"
msgid "vaggo tena pavuccatīti."
msgstr "and that’s how this chapter is recited."
